data.text:
Serving Horicon, Wisconsin since 1896

Horicon Bank proudly serves the people, families and businesses of Horicon, Wisconsin. Our bank headquarters were built in 1915 and is included in the National Register of Historic Places.

Whether you’re looking to open a savings or checking account, apply for a loan, or connect with a bank that has the technology you need to manage your finances, Horicon Bank is here to help!

Featured Service: Natural Choice Checking

When it comes to a personal banker, you want someone who is…well…personable. Matthew Peterson is more than happy to help you open a Natural Choice Checking account — a great option for students! — and explain what overdraft protection is all about.

Looking for something more robust? Matthew can help you navigate through our personal checking account options to find the product that’s right for you. Stop by the branch today or call him at 920-485-3040.

About Horicon Bank in Horicon, WI

Welcome to your digital community bank in Horicon, WI. Opened as our first location way back in 1896, you can find us near Horicon Marsh, Gold Star Memorial Trail, Dodge County Ledge Park, Wild Goose State Trail, Nitschke Mounds, Horicon Aquatic Center, and Horicon Hills. Look for our beautiful brick and limestone building. Our current building was constructed in 1915 and is listed on the National Register of Historic Places.

Founded on invention and built on community support, you can expect to find friendly tellers who are ready to help with all your banking transaction needs. With better banking options for our customers’ lives and a strong tie to our community roots, Horicon Bank is your digital community bank!

The Horicon branch supports local organizations like the Friends of Horicon Marsh Education and Visitor Center, Horicon Area Foundation, and Horicon Phoenix Group. We are also affiliated with the Horicon Chamber of Commerce.

Horicon Bank is the Natural Choice! Give us a call or visit our Horicon branch for lobby service or drive-up banking and our drive-up ATM. Learn why many consider us to be he best bank in Horicon!
